rotate-90 scale-0 transition-all dark:rotate-0 dark:scale-100 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button><a href=\"https://wa.me/2348137941914?text=Hi%20The%20Startup%20Desk%2C%20I&#x27;d%20like%20to%20talk%20about%20compliance%20for%20my%20startup.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg border border-whatsapp bg-whatsapp px-3.5 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-whatsapp-foreground transition-colors hover:bg-whatsapp/90\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.992 16.342a2 2 0 0 1 .094 1.167l-1.065 3.29a1 1 0 0 0 1.236 1.168l3.413-.998a2 2 0 0 1 1.099.092 10 10 0 1 0-4.777-4.719\"></path></svg>Talk to us</a></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 md:hidden relative z-[60]\"><button class=\"relative inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-primary/10 bg-white/80 dark:bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm text-primary transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105\" aria-label=\"Toggle visual theme mode\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sun h-[1.2rem] w-[1.2rem] rotate-0 scale-100 transition-all dark:-rotate-90 dark:scale-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon absolute h-[1.2rem] w-[1.2rem] rotate-90 scale-0 transition-all dark:rotate-0 dark:scale-100 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border bg-white dark:bg-black text-foreground transition-all focus:outline-none\" aria-label=\"Toggle Navigation Menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><div class=\"grid items-center gap-12 py-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-start space-y-6\"><span class=\"animate-fade-in-up inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-accent/20 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-primary\" style=\"animation-delay:80ms\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent animate-pulse\"></span>Compliance made effortless for founders</span><h1 class=\"animate-fade-in-up font-display text-4xl font-extrabold leading-[1.15] tracking-tight text-primary sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl\" style=\"animation-delay:160ms\">Compliance shouldn&#x27;t be the reason your startup<!-- --> <span class=\"animate-word-slide text-accent\"><span class=\"word-slider flex flex-col text-left\"><span>gets fined.</span><span>stalls growth.</span><span>loses momentum.</span></span></span></h1><p class=\"animate-fade-in-up max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground font-medium\" style=\"animation-delay:240ms\">We handle your CAC filings, tax registration, and the regulatory paperwork that trips founders up so you can stay focused on building, not battling deadlines.</p><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up flex w-full flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center\" style=\"animation-delay:320ms\"><a class=\"group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-accent px-7 py-3.5 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-lg transition-all hover:bg-accent/90 hover:scale-[1.02]\" href=\"/services\">Get Started<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://wa.me/2348137941914?text=Hi%20The%20Startup%20Desk%2C%20I&#x27;d%20like%20to%20talk%20about%20keeping%20my%20startup%20compliant.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2.5 rounded-xl bg-[#25D366] px-7 py-3.5 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-md transition-all hover:bg-[#20ba59] hover:scale-[1.02]\"><svg class=\"h-5 w-5 fill-current\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L0 24l6.335-1.662c1.746.953 3.71 1.455 5.703 1.458h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z\"></path></svg>Chat on WhatsApp</a></div><p class=\"animate-fade-in-up mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-muted-foreground/80\" style=\"animation-delay:400ms\">Trusted by early-stage teams across fintech, health, and commerce.</p></div><div class=\"hidden lg:block h-32\"></div></div><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up bg-white/40 border border-border/60 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4\" style=\"animation-delay:200ms\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-primary\">The gap nobody warns you about</h2><p class=\"text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed font-medium\">Most compliance problems start in your first few months because nobody hands you a clear manual. Google leaves you with ten different half answers and unexpected fines. We exist to close that gap plainly and consistently before it becomes a hazard.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"text-center\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-primary\">What we take off your plate</h2></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up bg-white border border-border p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:scale-[1.01] transition-transform\" style=\"animation-delay:100ms\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 bg-accent/10 text-accent rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-landmark h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M11.119 2.205a2 2 0 0 1 1.762 0l7.84 3.846A.5.5 0 0 1 20.5 7h-17a.5.5 0 0 1-.22-.949z\"></path><path d=\"M14 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M18 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M3 22h18\"></path><path d=\"M6 18v-7\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display font-bold text-lg text-primary\">CAC filings</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-2 leading-relaxed\">Registration, annual returns, and official entity status updates executed securely.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-accent mt-4 hover:underline\" href=\"/services\">Explore Launch Tiers <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up bg-white border border-border p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:scale-[1.01] transition-transform\" style=\"animation-delay:200ms\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 bg-accent/10 text-accent rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-check-corner h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10.5 22H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.706.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v6\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"m14 20 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display font-bold text-lg text-primary\">Tax registration</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-2 leading-relaxed\">Corporate TIN onboarding, VAT structures, and clean FIRS status records from day one.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-accent mt-4 hover:underline\" href=\"/services\">Explore Launch Tiers <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up bg-white border border-border p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:scale-[1.01] transition-transform\" style=\"animation-delay:300ms\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 bg-accent/10 text-accent rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-display font-bold text-lg text-primary\">Regulatory paperwork</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-2 leading-relaxed\">NDPA data mandates, industry operational licenses, and ongoing statutory timelines monitored.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-accent mt-4 hover:underline\" href=\"/services\">Explore Advisory Scope <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white/60 border border-border/80 rounded-3xl p-8 space-y-8\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-primary\">How it works</h2></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-4 text-center\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><span class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-accent block tracking-wider\">01</span><h4 class=\"font-display font-bold text-base text-primary\">Tell us your stage</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed px-2\">Brief our desk on your current incorporation metrics via a quick baseline query.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><span class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-accent block tracking-wider\">02</span><h4 class=\"font-display font-bold text-base text-primary\">We map requirements</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed px-2\">Our consulting layer extracts your exact sector obligations and pending filing tasks.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><span class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-accent block tracking-wider\">03</span><h4 class=\"font-display font-bold text-base text-primary\">We handle paperwork</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed px-2\">We prepare files, interface directly with registries, and clear backlogs cleanly.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><span class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-accent block tracking-wider\">04</span><h4 class=\"font-display font-bold text-base text-primary\">You stay covered</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed px-2\">Your structural frameworks stay secure under active monitoring routines.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up border border-dashed border-border bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4\" style=\"animation-delay:100ms\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-question-mark h-5 w-5 text-accent shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground font-semibold leading-relaxed\">The Startup Desk was built on an experienced legal compliance background to interpret regulation into plain, actionable checklists. We are a dedicated compliance consultancy, not an active law firm, meaning we focus entirely on corporate management paperwork frameworks rather than court litigation or representation.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white/40 border border-border p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-4\"><div><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl font-extrabold text-primary\">Compliance blueprints inside the hub</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1 font-medium\">Read comprehensive tutorials built to optimize early tracking indicators.</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-1.5 bg-primary hover:bg-primary/95 text-white font-bold text-xs px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl shadow-sm transition-all shrink-0\" href=\"/resources\">Browse all guides <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"bg-white border border-border/80 p-5 rounded-xl space-y-2 hover:border-accent/40 transition-colors\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-accent\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg> CAC &amp; Incorporation</div><h4 class=\"font-display font-bold text-sm text-primary\">CAC Annual Returns: What Happens If You Don&#x27;t File</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Discover how missing statutory reporting metrics triggers structural registry drop deletion risks.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white border border-border/80 p-5 rounded-xl space-y-2 hover:border-accent/40 transition-colors\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-accent\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg> Data Protection</div><h4 class=\"font-display font-bold text-sm text-primary\">NDPA Basics: What Every Startup Needs to Know</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Clean, split breakdowns of user metadata tracking boundaries designed for operational software modules.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-primary px-6 py-12 text-center text-primary-foreground shadow-xl md:px-12\" style=\"animation-delay:200ms\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0\"><div class=\"absolute -right-16 -top-16 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-accent/10 blur-xl\"></div></div><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl\">Ready to stop guessing what is required?</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-white/80 max-w-xl mx-auto\">Get your corporate registry frameworks configured and audited cleanly before structural limits block your next transaction phase.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4\"><a class=\"inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-accent px-7 py-3.5 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-accent/90 transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]\" href=\"/services\">Get Started <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://wa.me/2348137941914\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-[#25D366] px-7 py-3.5 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-[#20ba59] transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.992 16.342a2 2 0 0 1 .094 1.167l-1.065 3.29a1 1 0 0 0 1.236 1.168l3.413-.998a2 2 0 0 1 1.099.092 10 10 0 1 0-4.777-4.719\"></path></svg> Chat on WhatsApp</a></div></div></div></section><footer class=\"border-t border-border bg-muted/40 mt-auto\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]\"><div class=\"max-w-sm space-y-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary text-primary-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"font-display text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary\">The Startup Desk</span></a><p class=\"text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\">Compliance handled from your first CAC filing to your first funding round. A compliance consultancy for early-stage Nigerian startups, not a law firm.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary\">Explore</p><ul class=\"mt-4 flex flex-col gap-3 text-xs font-semibold\"><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/services\">Services</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/resources\">Resources Hub</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary\">Legal &amp; Compliance</p><ul class=\"mt-4 flex flex-col gap-3 text-xs font-semibold\"><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a></